{"tid":1740564,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"被卡雲尼挑釁隻揪　美斯︰隨時奉陪","createTime":"2019-11-20T03:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T12:07:46.000Z","uid":98659,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"048fcf7e661f53d1ccc2d3c475ddf5d5962fe3c0","tid":1740564,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:31:58.000Z","msg":"阿根廷球星美斯周一在補時射入12碼，協助阿根廷在國際友賽以2:2逼和烏拉圭，不過美斯在比賽中與為烏拉圭先開紀錄的卡雲尼疑似爆發衝突，充滿火藥味。<br />\n<br />\n據阿根廷報章《Ole》報道，從電視畫面可以看到，卡雲尼在這場於以色列進行的比賽上半場尾段疑似挑釁美斯，表示想與對方打架，《Ole》更聲稱美斯以「隨時奉陪」作回應，烏拉圭後衞高甸則伸手搭着美斯肩膀嘗試緩和局面。<br />\n<br />\n不過，卡雲尼賽後淡化事件，《ESPN》引述他說︰「這是一場經典、非常激烈的南美足球的比賽。雙方表現都很好，我們都帶着正面的感覺比賽，我們都努力去踢足球，很正常。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/fyOEb1CNnqgeY7E0vumCPsNRx-Q=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/BTPQ7GAI4QBSHCKE2XCO7FWA5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FfyOEb1CNnqgeY7E0vumCPsNRx-Q%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FBTPQ7GAI4QBSHCKE2XCO7FWA5M.jpg&h=ea23375c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191119/HYBB45XJW3JA3LYV6CDYO3DF4Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191119%2FHYBB45XJW3JA3LYV6CDYO3DF4Y%2F&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNt%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=9a600cda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191119%2FHYBB45XJW3JA3LYV6CDYO3DF4Y%2F&h=f6608fe1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191119/HYBB45XJW3JA3LYV6CDYO3DF4Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n隻揪啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"84528328f1f800a7cc947696c75350f742cf1823","tid":1740564,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"so9個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal